<div class="content means imeans" data-group="imeans" id="basicmean-wrapper">
    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <p><strong>1. <a href="#vfsfeemj">当真[dàngzhēn]</a></strong><strong>2. <a href="#nrouqozu">当真[dàngzhēn]</a></strong></p><dl><dt><a name="#vfsfeemj">当真[dàngzhēn]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>[take seriously;accept as true] 信以为真</p><p>我只是开个玩笑,何必当真</p></li></ol></dd></dl><dl><dt><a name="#nrouqozu">当真[dàngzhēn]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>[really;really true] 确实,果然</p><p>队长,明天当真要上野猪窟开荒造田么</p><p>没过几天,他当真给我送来了一盆水仙花</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
